name: Young Stoner Life | Cannabis/Weed Dispensary | Patong Phuket Thailand
description: Cannabis dispensary located in Patong, Phuket, Thailand. We specialise in bringing our costumers the highest, cleanest and tastiest buds. We offer cannabis from California and Canada, as well as the best grown weed in Thailand. Come check us out, you will not be disappointed.

The owner is from the Netherlands, so he knows a thing or two about the quality of flowers/buds.
